-- UBS Hires Goldman’s Molin for Hedge-Fund Relationship Post
-- B y   L a u r a   M a r c i n e k
-- 2012-04-19T19:57:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-19/ubs-appoints-goldman-s-scott-molin-for-hedge-fund-relationships.html
UBS AG (UBSN) ’s equities division for the
Americas added Scott Molin, who previously worked at  Goldman
Sachs Group Inc. (GS) , as a managing director in its senior
relationship-management team.  Molin will focus on hedge funds, according to an internal
employee memo obtained by Bloomberg News. At Goldman Sachs, he
was co-head of the firm’s cross assets sales group to hedge
funds, and before that worked in equity research sales at
Donaldson, Lufkin & Jenrette, UBS said in the memo said.  Christiaan Brakman, a spokesman for the Zurich-based bank,
declined to comment beyond confirming the memo’s contents.  To contact the reporter on this story:
